---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { GHL_WEBHOOK_URL } from '../lib/ghl';
import HomeReviews from '../components/HomeReviews.astro';
---
<Layout title="Home Value Report — Stairway Mortgage" description="See what your home is worth today — plus your equity, what you can do with it, neighborhood trends, and a private hub to manage your home. Free, no obligation.">

<div class="hvr-scope">

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hvr-hero">
  <div class="hvr-container">
    <div class="hvr-hero-grid">
      <div>
        <span class="hvr-eyebrow">Free Tools · Home Value</span>
        <h1>What is your home<br><em>worth today?</em></h1>
        <p class="hvr-lede">Get an instant home value report — then go deeper. See your equity, what you can do with it, what's happening in your neighborhood, and a private hub to manage your home. All in one place, all free.</p>
        <ul class="hvr-hero-points">
          <li>Live value estimate with low–high range, updated monthly</li>
          <li>Your equity and what it can do — refinance, cash-out, invest</li>
          <li>Neighborhood trends, school ratings, and project ROI</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="hvr-trust-line">Jim Blackburn · NMLS&nbsp;#1072866 · 5.0★ · Free, no obligation</p>
      </div>
      <div class="hvr-formcard" id="hvr-top">
        <h2>Get your free report</h2>
        <p class="hvr-form-sub">Enter your details and we'll send you instant access to your full home value report.</p>
        <div id="hvr-form" data-ghl-endpoint={GHL_WEBHOOK_URL}>
          <div class="hvr-error hvr-hidden" id="hvr-error"></div>
          <div class="hvr-field hvr-field-row">
            <div><label class="hvr-label" for="hvr-first">First name</label><input class="hvr-input" type="text" id="hvr-first" placeholder="First" autocomplete="given-name"></div>
            <div><label class="hvr-label" for="hvr-last">Last name</label><input class="hvr-input" type="text" id="hvr-last" placeholder="Last" autocomplete="family-name"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="hvr-field"><label class="hvr-label" for="hvr-email">Email</label><input class="hvr-input" type="email" id="hvr-email" placeholder="you@email.com" autocomplete="email"></div>
          <div class="hvr-field"><label class="hvr-label" for="hvr-address">Property address</label><input class="hvr-input hvr-address-input" type="text" id="hvr-address" placeholder="Start typing your address…" autocomplete="off"></div>
          <div class="hvr-field"><label class="hvr-label" for="hvr-phone">Phone <span class="hvr-opt">— optional</span></label><input class="hvr-input" type="tel" id="hvr-phone" placeholder="(555) 555-5555" autocomplete="tel"><p class="hvr-opt-note">Only if you want us to call you. No pressure — leave it blank otherwise.</p></div>
          <input type="text" name="_gotcha" id="hvr-gotcha" style="position:absolute;left:-9999px;opacity:0;" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" aria-hidden="true">
          <button class="hvr-btn" type="button" id="hvr-submit">See My Home Value
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg>
          </button>
          <p class="hvr-form-foot">Free, no obligation. We do not sell your information.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hvr-success hvr-hidden" id="hvr-success">
          <div class="hvr-check"><svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg></div>
          <h3>Check your email.</h3>
          <p>We've sent a verification link to confirm your email. Here's what happens next:</p>
          <div class="hvr-step"><div class="hvr-step-n">1</div><p>Open the email from us and click <strong>verify</strong>.</p></div>
          <div class="hvr-step"><div class="hvr-step-n">2</div><p>We'll send your private report link.</p></div>
          <div class="hvr-step"><div class="hvr-step-n">3</div><p>See your full home value report instantly.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- THE REPORT — split section -->
<section class="hvr-section">
  <div class="hvr-container">
    <div class="hvr-split">
      <div>
        <span class="hvr-eyebrow">The Report</span>
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:400;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-0.015em;margin:18px 0 0;">More than a number. <em style="font-style:italic;color:var(--blue);font-weight:500;">A full picture.</em></h2>
        <p style="font-size:1.125rem;color:var(--ink-light);margin:18px 0 0;">Most "what's my home worth" tools hand you a single estimate and stop. Yours opens a complete view of your home as a financial asset — value, equity, and exactly what you can do with it.</p>
        <ul class="hvr-deliver">
          <li><span class="n">01</span><div><div class="t">Live value estimate + range</div><div class="d">A current market value with a low–high range, plus how it's changed since you bought. Refreshed every month automatically.</div></div></li>
          <li><span class="n">02</span><div><div class="t">Your equity, calculated</div><div class="d">How much equity you've built, shown as a dollar figure and a percentage of your home's value.</div></div></li>
          <li><span class="n">03</span><div><div class="t">What your equity can do</div><div class="d">Purchasing power for a new home, a cash-out, or an investment property — and ideas like consolidating debt or funding a project.</div></div></li>
          <li><span class="n">04</span><div><div class="t">Refinance &amp; payment breakdown</div><div class="d">See principal vs. interest, lifetime interest, and what extra payments or a refinance could save you.</div></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="hvr-split-visual">
        <div class="hvr-dash">
          <div class="hvr-dash-tag">Sample report</div>
          <div class="hvr-dash-bar"><i></i><i></i><i></i><span class="hvr-dash-url">your-home-value-report</span></div>
          <div class="hvr-dash-body">
            <div class="hvr-dash-addr">Your Home · Current Estimate</div>
            <div class="hvr-dash-value">$487,500</div>
            <div class="hvr-dash-delta"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="18 15 12 9 6 15"></polyline></svg> +$42,300 since purchase</div>
            <div class="hvr-dash-range">Low $451,200 — High $523,800 · Updated monthly</div>
            <div class="hvr-spark">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 320 90" width="100%" height="90" preserveAspectRatio="none" role="img" aria-label="Estimated value trend over time">
                <defs><linearGradient id="hvrGrad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#1845D6" stop-opacity="0.18"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#1845D6" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient></defs>
                <path d="M0,70 L40,66 L80,58 L120,60 L160,48 L200,42 L240,34 L280,26 L320,18 L320,90 L0,90 Z" fill="url(#hvrGrad)"/>
                <path d="M0,70 L40,66 L80,58 L120,60 L160,48 L200,42 L240,34 L280,26 L320,18" fill="none" stroke="#1845D6" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                <circle cx="320" cy="18" r="4" fill="#1845D6"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="hvr-dash-cards">
              <div class="hvr-dash-card"><div class="l">Your Equity</div><div class="n">$163,900</div></div>
              <div class="hvr-dash-card"><div class="l">Cash-Out Power</div><div class="n">$98,500</div></div>
              <div class="hvr-dash-card"><div class="l">Remodel Upside</div><div class="n">$71,200</div></div>
              <div class="hvr-dash-card"><div class="l">New-Home Power</div><div class="n">$612K</div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mute);text-align:center;margin-top:14px;">Sample figures shown · your real numbers after sign-up</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- EQUITY DONUT + BAR CHARTS -->
<section class="hvr-section hvr-section-tint">
  <div class="hvr-container">
    <div class="hvr-split rev">
      <div class="hvr-split-visual">
        <div class="hvr-viz" style="margin-bottom:18px;">
          <div class="hvr-viz-title">Equity in your home</div>
          <div class="hvr-donut-wrap">
            <div class="hvr-donut">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 42 42" width="132" height="132">
                <circle cx="21" cy="21" r="15.915" fill="none" stroke="#EDEDE5" stroke-width="6"></circle>
                <circle cx="21" cy="21" r="15.915" fill="none" stroke="#2E9E2E" stroke-width="6" stroke-dasharray="34 66" stroke-dashoffset="25" stroke-linecap="round"></circle>
              </svg>
              <div class="center"><b>34%</b><span>Equity</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="hvr-donut-legend">
              <div><i style="background:#2E9E2E;"></i> Your equity — $163,900</div>
              <div><i style="background:#EDEDE5;"></i> Remaining balance — $323,600</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hvr-viz">
          <div class="hvr-viz-title">What your equity can do</div>
          <div class="hvr-bars">
            <div><div class="hvr-bar-top"><span>New-home purchasing power</span><b>$612K</b></div><div class="hvr-bar-track"><div class="hvr-bar-fill" style="width:100%;"></div></div></div>
            <div><div class="hvr-bar-top"><span>Cash-out available</span><b>$98.5K</b></div><div class="hvr-bar-track"><div class="hvr-bar-fill" style="width:42%;"></div></div></div>
            <div><div class="hvr-bar-top"><span>Investment property down</span><b>$80K</b></div><div class="hvr-bar-track"><div class="hvr-bar-fill" style="width:34%;"></div></div></div>
            <div><div class="hvr-bar-top"><span>Debt you could consolidate</span><b>$36K</b></div><div class="hvr-bar-track"><div class="hvr-bar-fill" style="width:18%;background:var(--gold);"></div></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="hvr-eyebrow">Build Wealth</span>
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:400;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-0.015em;margin:18px 0 0;">Your equity is doing <em style="font-style:italic;color:var(--blue);font-weight:500;">more than you think.</em></h2>
        <p style="font-size:1.125rem;color:var(--ink-light);margin:18px 0 0;">Equity sitting in your home is a tool — for a move, an investment, a renovation, or wiping out high-interest debt. Your report shows exactly how much you have and lays out, in plain numbers, what each path looks like for <em>your</em> home.</p>
        <p style="font-size:1.0625rem;color:var(--ink-2);margin:18px 0 0;">And when you want to talk through the smartest move, our team is one click away — no pressure, no obligation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- IMPROVE & COMPARE -->
<section class="hvr-section">
  <div class="hvr-container">
    <div class="hvr-split">
      <div>
        <span class="hvr-eyebrow">Improve &amp; Compare</span>
        <h2 style="font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:400;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-0.015em;margin:18px 0 0;">Know which upgrades <em style="font-style:italic;color:var(--blue);font-weight:500;">pay you back.</em></h2>
        <p style="font-size:1.125rem;color:var(--ink-light);margin:18px 0 0;">Thinking about a remodel? Your report ranks projects by real return on investment and estimates local costs — so you spend where it counts. Plus a live read on your neighborhood's market so you always know where you stand.</p>
        <ul class="hvr-deliver">
          <li><span class="n">→</span><div><div class="t">Project ROI, ranked</div><div class="d">See potential value added by each upgrade, highest-return first.</div></div></li>
          <li><span class="n">→</span><div><div class="t">Local cost estimates</div><div class="d">Budget accurately with estimates tuned to your area.</div></div></li>
          <li><span class="n">→</span><div><div class="t">Neighborhood market trends</div><div class="d">Median prices, days on market, and buyer-vs-seller demand.</div></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="hvr-split-visual">
        <div class="hvr-viz" style="margin-bottom:18px;">
          <div class="hvr-viz-title">Top projects by return</div>
          <div class="hvr-roi">
            <div class="hvr-roi-row"><div class="hvr-roi-label"><span>Add a full bath</span><b>+$37,870 · 10.2%</b></div><div class="hvr-roi-track"><div class="hvr-roi-fill" style="width:100%;"></div></div></div>
            <div class="hvr-roi-row"><div class="hvr-roi-label"><span>Luxury kitchen remodel</span><b>+$17,025 · 4.6%</b></div><div class="hvr-roi-track"><div class="hvr-roi-fill" style="width:45%;"></div></div></div>
            <div class="hvr-roi-row"><div class="hvr-roi-label"><span>Luxury bath remodel</span><b>+$14,540 · 3.9%</b></div><div class="hvr-roi-track"><div class="hvr-roi-fill" style="width:38%;"></div></div></div>
            <div class="hvr-roi-row"><div class="hvr-roi-label"><span>Add a bedroom</span><b>+$12,166 · 3.3%</b></div><div class="hvr-roi-track"><div class="hvr-roi-fill" style="width:32%;"></div></div></div>
            <div class="hvr-roi-row"><div class="hvr-roi-label"><span>Attached one-car garage</span><b>+$6,305 · 1.7%</b></div><div class="hvr-roi-track"><div class="hvr-roi-fill" style="width:17%;"></div></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hvr-viz">
          <div class="hvr-viz-title">Your neighborhood right now</div>
          <div class="hvr-market">
            <div class="hvr-market-cell"><div class="l">Median list price</div><div class="n">$439,695</div></div>
            <div class="hvr-market-cell"><div class="l">Days on market</div><div class="n">59</div></div>
            <div class="hvr-market-cell"><div class="l">Active inventory</div><div class="n">88</div></div>
            <div class="hvr-market-cell"><div class="l">Market demand</div><div class="n" style="font-size:1.05rem;">Balanced</div><div class="s">Stable conditions</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INCLUDED FREE — 6 image cards -->
<section class="hvr-section hvr-section-tint">
  <div class="hvr-container">
    <div class="hvr-section-head">
      <span class="hvr-eyebrow">Included Free</span>
      <h2>And it doesn't stop at the <em>value.</em></h2>
      <p>Your report comes with a private hub to understand your neighborhood, plan smart projects, and manage your home year-round. Here's everything waiting on the other side.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hvr-grid">
      <div class="hvr-fcard">
        <img class="hvr-fcard-img" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/106399/pexels-photo-106399.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=900" alt="Suburban neighborhood homes" loading="lazy" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/720x450/1845D6/FFFFFF/png?text=Neighborhood+Trends';">
        <div class="hvr-fcard-body"><h3>Neighborhood trends</h3><p>See what's really happening on your street and ZIP.</p><ul><li>Median list &amp; sale prices, price per sq ft</li><li>Days on market and current inventory</li><li>Buyer vs. seller market demand</li></ul></div>
      </div>
      <div class="hvr-fcard">
        <img class="hvr-fcard-img" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/8500355/pexels-photo-8500355.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=900" alt="Students walking to school" loading="lazy" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/720x450/1845D6/FFFFFF/png?text=School+Ratings';">
        <div class="hvr-fcard-body"><h3>School &amp; lifestyle scores</h3><p>The data buyers and families care about most.</p><ul><li>District score and individual school ratings</li><li>Walkability, family-friendly, and more</li><li>Student–teacher ratios and spending</li></ul></div>
      </div>
      <div class="hvr-fcard">
        <img class="hvr-fcard-img" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1599791/pexels-photo-1599791.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=900" alt="Modern renovated kitchen" loading="lazy" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/720x450/1845D6/FFFFFF/png?text=Project+ROI';">
        <div class="hvr-fcard-body"><h3>Project value &amp; ROI</h3><p>Know which upgrades actually pay you back.</p><ul><li>Current value vs. potential after remodel</li><li>Ranked projects by return on investment</li><li>Local project cost estimates for your area</li></ul></div>
      </div>
      <div class="hvr-fcard">
        <img class="hvr-fcard-img" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1571460/pexels-photo-1571460.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=900" alt="Family home exterior" loading="lazy" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/720x450/1845D6/FFFFFF/png?text=Manage+Your+Home';">
        <div class="hvr-fcard-body"><h3>Your home, managed</h3><p>One place for everything you own.</p><ul><li>Property timeline: history, sales, taxes</li><li>Home inventory with maintenance reminders</li><li>Repair tracking and document storage</li></ul></div>
      </div>
      <div class="hvr-fcard">
        <img class="hvr-fcard-img" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/8961065/pexels-photo-8961065.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=900" alt="Contractor at work" loading="lazy" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/720x450/1845D6/FFFFFF/png?text=Vetted+Local+Pros';">
        <div class="hvr-fcard-body"><h3>Vetted local pros</h3><p>Trusted help when you need it.</p><ul><li>Plumbers, electricians, contractors, cleaners</li><li>Recommended by your advisors</li><li>Compare and connect in a click</li></ul></div>
      </div>
      <div class="hvr-fcard">
        <img class="hvr-fcard-img" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/4386431/pexels-photo-4386431.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=900" alt="Advisor reviewing finances with clients" loading="lazy" onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='https://placehold.co/720x450/1845D6/FFFFFF/png?text=Mortgage+Guidance';">
        <div class="hvr-fcard-body"><h3>Mortgage &amp; refi guidance</h3><p>Real answers from a real loan officer.</p><ul><li>Payment and extra-payment savings tools</li><li>Refinance scenarios for your situation</li><li>Direct line to our team — when you want it</li></ul></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS BAND -->
<section class="hvr-section hvr-section-ink">
  <div class="hvr-container">
    <div class="hvr-stats">
      <div class="hvr-stat"><div class="num"><em>$500M+</em></div><div class="label">In closed loans</div></div>
      <div class="hvr-stat"><div class="num">7×</div><div class="label">Scotsman Guide Top Producer</div></div>
      <div class="hvr-stat"><div class="num">5.0★</div><div class="label">Client rating</div></div>
      <div class="hvr-stat"><div class="num">24<span style="font-size:1.4rem;">hr</span></div><div class="label">Typical response</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MID-PAGE 2ND CAPTURE FORM -->
<section class="hvr-section">
  <div class="hvr-container">
    <div class="hvr-capture2">
      <div>
        <span class="hvr-eyebrow">Ready When You Are</span>
        <h2>See your full report in <em>about a minute.</em></h2>
        <p class="lede">No cost, no commitment, and we never sell your information. Just your home's real numbers and everything you need to make smart moves with them.</p>
        <ul class="pts"><li>Instant value, equity, and what it can do</li><li>Neighborhood, schools, and project ROI</li><li>A private hub to manage your home all year</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="hvr-formcard" style="color:var(--ink);">
        <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;">Start your free report</h2>
        <p class="hvr-form-sub">Takes under a minute. We'll email your private report link.</p>
        <div class="hvr-field hvr-field-row">
          <div><label class="hvr-label" for="hvr2-first">First name</label><input class="hvr-input" type="text" id="hvr2-first" placeholder="First" autocomplete="given-name"></div>
          <div><label class="hvr-label" for="hvr2-last">Last name</label><input class="hvr-input" type="text" id="hvr2-last" placeholder="Last" autocomplete="family-name"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hvr-field"><label class="hvr-label" for="hvr2-email">Email</label><input class="hvr-input" type="email" id="hvr2-email" placeholder="you@email.com" autocomplete="email"></div>
        <div class="hvr-field"><label class="hvr-label" for="hvr2-address">Property address</label><input class="hvr-input hvr-address-input" type="text" id="hvr2-address" placeholder="Start typing your address…" autocomplete="off"></div>
        <div class="hvr-field"><label class="hvr-label" for="hvr2-phone">Phone <span class="hvr-opt">— optional</span></label><input class="hvr-input" type="tel" id="hvr2-phone" placeholder="(555) 555-5555" autocomplete="tel"><p class="hvr-opt-note">Only if you want us to call you.</p></div>
        <button class="hvr-btn" type="button" id="hvr2-submit">See My Home Value
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline></svg>
        </button>
        <p class="hvr-form-foot">Free, no obligation. We do not sell your information. NMLS&nbsp;#1072866.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="hvr-section hvr-section-tint">
  <div class="hvr-container">
    <div class="hvr-section-head"><span class="hvr-eyebrow">Good To Know</span><h2>Questions, <em>answered.</em></h2></div>
    <div class="hvr-faq">
      <div class="hvr-faq-item"><p class="hvr-faq-q">Is this really free?</p><p class="hvr-faq-a">Yes — completely. There's no cost, no obligation, and no credit pull. The report and the home management hub are free for you to use as long as you like.</p></div>
      <div class="hvr-faq-item"><p class="hvr-faq-q">How accurate is the value estimate?</p><p class="hvr-faq-a">It's a market-based estimate drawn from comparable sales and current conditions, shown with a low–high range. It's a strong starting point — and when you want a precise figure, our team can prepare a personalized analysis for your exact property.</p></div>
      <div class="hvr-faq-item"><p class="hvr-faq-q">Do I have to talk to anyone?</p><p class="hvr-faq-a">Not at all. Phone is optional — leave it blank and you'll still get your full report. If you'd like to talk through your options, add your number and we'll reach out. Your call.</p></div>
      <div class="hvr-faq-item"><p class="hvr-faq-q">Will you sell my information?</p><p class="hvr-faq-a">Never. Your details stay with our team and are used only to deliver your report and follow up if you ask us to.</p></div>
      <div class="hvr-faq-item"><p class="hvr-faq-q">What happens after I enter my email?</p><p class="hvr-faq-a">We'll send a quick verification link to confirm it's you. Click it, and we'll send your private report link — your full report opens instantly.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
